  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Sentient Vessel Storage Sac",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "有感知力的飞船存储囊",
    "TraditionalChinese": "感知太空船倉儲卵囊"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "An <span class=\"name name-special\">additional storage nodule</span> for <span class=\"name name-technology\">Sentient</span> starships. Upon hatching, the parasite inside this sac is grafted upon the vessel, exchanging the use of its cavernous innards for vital nutrients from the host.<br><br>Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to trigger growth and begin the <VAL_ON>hatching process<>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个<span class=\"name name-special\">额外的储存结点</span>，用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">有感知力的</span>飞船。孵化后，这个囊中的寄生虫会被嫁接到容器上，它的内脏会转换为宿主的重要营养。<br><br>使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>来触发生长，开始<VAL_ON>孵化过程<>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個<span class=\"name name-special\">知覺</span>太空船的<span class=\"name name-technology\">額外倉儲結節</span>。孵化時，卵囊內的寄生蟲會寄生到船艙上，利用其海綿狀的內部構造與宿主交換重要養分。<br><br>按下 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 以觸發成長，並開始<VAL_ON>孵化過程<>。"
  },
